      "updated": 1783162749887,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Dowwnload video Segments\n(Adaptive Bitrate Streaming)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "BaWM5IX-Yeqe8KVS96lDH",
      "originalText": "Dowwnload video Segments\n(Adaptive Bitrate Streaming)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RO894Vkuy8OtWg4EFfJb0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 541.9951846693245,
      "y": 1830.9866719045147,
      "width": 1094.4390869140625,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b02",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1546555473,
      "version": 77,
      "versionNonce": 1112251985,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783163503480,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Adaptive Bitrate Streaming (Simple Notes)\n- A video is split into many small segments (chunks).\n- Multiple versions of each segment are created (e.g., 1080p, 720p, 480p).\n- During upload, a manifest file is created.\n- The manifest file acts like an index/map that contains links to all video segments and their available qualities.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Adaptive Bitrate Streaming (Simple Notes)\n- A video is split into many small segments (chunks).\n- Multiple versions of each segment are created (e.g., 1080p, 720p, 480p).\n- During upload, a manifest file is created.\n- The manifest file acts like an index/map that contains links to all video segments and their available qualities.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MZB4dwF6n5plH-k15369T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -543.1409123784645,
      "y": 2029.8583758605193,
      "width": 320.759765625,
      "height": 475,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b03",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1995899889,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 1149860785,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783163520602,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "User Uploads Video\n    ↓\nS3 Stores Original Video\n    ↓\nS3 Event Notification\n    ↓\nVideo Processing Service\n    ↓\nCreate Multiple Qualities\n(1080p, 720p, 480p)\n    ↓\nSplit Each Quality into Segments\n    ↓\nGenerate Manifest File\n    ↓\nStore Segments + Manifest in S3\n    ↓\nUpdate VideoMetadata\n(with Manifest URL)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "User Uploads Video\n    ↓\nS3 Stores Original Video\n    ↓\nS3 Event Notification\n    ↓\nVideo Processing Service\n    ↓\nCreate Multiple Qualities\n(1080p, 720p, 480p)\n    ↓\nSplit Each Quality into Segments\n    ↓\nGenerate Manifest File\n    ↓\nStore Segments + Manifest in S3\n    ↓\nUpdate VideoMetadata\n(with Manifest URL)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dCPGZCcdjoMvLfClsI2kB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 501.42251544981195,
      "y": 2085.1994846196344,
      "width": 1015.9592895507812,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b04",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2014547007,
      "version": 87,
